snippet.title: Warriors of the Nile 2 TGS2021 Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1682060/Warriors_of_the_Nile_2/
Full game available in 2022 on Steam
The sequel of Warriors of the Nile keeps its feature as a fast-paced strategy roguelite game. Demo available today, grab and play it now!
